Chemical Engineer

Brunel

- Reno, NV

We are hiring a Chemical Engineer for our client, a successful mining company breaking into the US market. This is a full time permanent role with a great opportunity to be part of a new large-scale construction project of a chemical plant. This individual will work closely with the mining department teams to assist in the mining and development of Phosphate materials daily.
About you
Requirements
Bachelor's Degree in Engineering is required
Experience in the Mining field is an asset
A strong background in chemistry, physics, biology and mathematics is required
Strong experience working with Phosphate products
Strong knowledge of Lithium products
Solid understanding of inorganic chemistry
